            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Gunfredus">Gumfrid</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Baruncius">Baruncio</name></persName> germani
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Baroccius">Baruccii</name></persName>
                        <foreign>promettono a</foreign>
                        <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName> in Dei nomine
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa</rs> seo et res illa quem nobis ad resedendo dedisti in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/36"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns"
                            >Saltuclo</placeName>, casa cum curte, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >orto</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">terris</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Acorns">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivitis</rs>, omnia ad
                        ipsa casa pertenente, qualiter ipsa casa Baruccio ad manum suam habuit,
                        nobis ad resedendo et melliorando dedisti, in tali tenure, ut per omne annum
                        tibi reddere debeamus <rs key="#Rent_in_money">uno soldo bono
                            expendibile</rs> et <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">medietate vino</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Operae">angaria</rs> ad <rs key="#Demesnes">sundro domnico</rs>
                        facere debeamus, qualis ibidem utilitas fuerit in ipso loco <rs
                            key="#Demesnes #Operae">Saltuclo</rs>. <foreign>Pena in caso di
                            inadempienza alle promesse o</foreign> se aut ipsa casa vel res
                        meliorata non fuerit, aut nos de ipsa casa exierimus alibi habitando,
                        spondemus (…) essemus conpunituri pena nomine auri soldos viginti, et
                        exeamus de ipsa res nanis et vacui. <foreign>Peredeo promette ai due
                            fratelli in base alle stesse clausole e di non</foreign> de predicta
                        casa vel res foris mittere (…) aut aliqua superpositione facere (…) pena
                        nomine auri soldos numero viginti. Et duas pagina un tenure conscripte
                            <persName key="#Writer #Subdeacons"><name ref="Fratellus"
                                >Fratellus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs> scrivere rogavimus. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: +
                        Gunfrid promissoris; + Baruncio germano eius promissoris; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gumbrandus">Gumprandi</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Auselmus">Auselmi</name></persName> testis; +
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Aregis">Aruchis</name></persName>
                        germani eius testis; + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Georgius"
                                >Georgi</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Rotius"
                                >Rotti</name></persName> testis. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>:
                        Fratellus subdiaconus.</ab>
                        </div>
